HOW TO RUN
──────────
Just double-click any .html file to open it in your browser.
No server, no internet, no installation needed.
 
Or in VS Code:
  1. Install the "Live Server" extension (optional, but nicer)
  2. Right-click the .html file → "Open with Live Server"
  OR simply press Ctrl+Shift+P → "Open in Default Browser"
 
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
TASK 1 — Task1_LanguageTranslation.html
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Tool: Language Translation Tool
Tech: Built-in bilingual dictionary (500+ entries) + sentence
      tokenizer + multi-language phrase engine
Langs: English, Spanish, French, German, Italian, Portuguese,
       Hindi, Telugu, Arabic, Russian, Japanese, Chinese
Features:
  • Translate full sentences and paragraphs
  • Swap source/target languages
  • Text-to-speech (read translation aloud)
  • Copy to clipboard
  • Quick phrase buttons (30+ common phrases)
  • Ctrl+Enter keyboard shortcut